      "content": "hey so i was prescribed some antibiotics for this skin infection i had but i've only been taking them for 3 days and my skin looks totally normal now like the redness is completely gone. is it okay if i just stop taking them now? i dont really want to keep putting chemicals in my body if i dont need to",
