      "content": "i get that, but my doctor didn't really explain why i have to finish the whole thing if the infection is gone. it just feels like a waste of medicine and i'm worried about the side effects of taking it for 7 more days if i'm already healthy. can't i just take a double dose tomorrow to make up for the days i missed if i decide to stop now?",
